      },
      "rationale": "SST k-ω selected after comparison with k-ε realizable and LES (coarse) on the FDA GCBP geometry. SST k-ω achieves lowest NIH NRMSE (8.7% vs 14.2% for k-ε, 9.1% for LES-coarse). Hemolysis power-law constants (C=1.8×10⁻⁶, α=0.765, β=2.416) calibrated to Zhang et al. (2011) bovine RBC data. Model form uncertainty contribution to total NIH uncertainty: 31% of total variance per Sobol decomposition."
